       after import using _r_._s_u_p_p_o_r_t or _r_._r_e_g_i_o_n.


       The  ggaammmmaa option is only used if the image contains a gamma specifica-
       tion.


       The aallpphhaa option is only relevant if the  image  contains  transparency
       information.

